Welcome to Tailgate. This documentation will help you get started with our platform.

## Getting started

To get started follow these steps:

1. Sign up for an account on the website.
2. Complete your profile setup.
3. Start exploring the platform features.

## Features

Tailgate provides the following features:
1. User authentication
2. Account management
3. Team collaboration
4. And more!
